Package: snirh.lab
Type: Package
Title: Convert Laboratory Water-Quality Data to SNIRH Import Format
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-09-20
Authors@R: c(
    person("LuÃ­s", "Pereira", , "d57177@alunos.uevora.pt", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0628-4847"))
  )
Description: Tools to convert tidy laboratory analytical results into the
    official batch-import format used by Portugal's National Water Resources
    Information System (SNIRH). Functions validate station identifiers, map
    parameters and units, and generate CSV files for surface water, ground
    water, biota, and sediment. Designed for use with 'data.table' and
    compatible with reproducible workflows.
